(firstQuint)Cardiac Arrest Registry of the Province of Pavia (Pavia CARe).

 The registry is an observational study which enroll all the patients who suffered an out-of-hospital cardiac arrest of any etiology in the Province of Pavia.

 The follow-up of the patients is at 1 month after the event, 6 month and every year up to five years after the event.

